issue.title: Update toolchain to GCC 4.9
issue.body:
This unblocks several issues, from https://github.com/PX4/Firmware/pull/13336#event-2761014645
to https://github.com/PX4/Matrix/pull/100#issuecomment-545363732

Not tested, since I don't have a RPi handy at the moment.

@dagar
